cs.CV, cs.CL, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.IR. 

The paper is about scene text recognition, which is a computer vision task, hence cs.CV is the most likely category. The paper also involves natural language processing techniques such as sequence-to-sequence models and self-attention, which are covered in cs.CL. The paper proposes a new model architecture that relies on parallelization and less complexity, which falls under the category of machine learning, specifically deep learning, hence cs.LG and cs.AI are also likely categories. Finally, the paper deals with text recognition, which is a subfield of information retrieval, hence cs.IR is also a possible category.
